%% Satın alma akışı sequence diagram.
%% Idempotency-Key + webhook signing güzergahı dahil.

sequenceDiagram
    actor Aday
    participant FE as Frontend (SPA)
    participant API as Backend (NestJS)
    participant Redis
    participant Pg as PostgreSQL
    participant Iyzico as Iyzico / Stripe

    Aday->>FE: "Satın al" butonu
    FE->>FE: uuid() → Idempotency-Key üret
    FE->>API: POST /v1/purchases<br/>Idempotency-Key: <uuid><br/>Body: { testId, ... }

    Note over API: IdempotencyInterceptor
    API->>Redis: GET idem:<tenant>:<user>:<key>
    Redis-->>API: null (yok)
    API->>Redis: SET NX EX 60s<br/>{ status: 'in_progress', hash }
    Redis-->>API: OK

    Note over API: PurchaseUseCase
    API->>Pg: BEGIN TX
    API->>Pg: SELECT package WHERE id, tenantId
    API->>Pg: SELECT FOR UPDATE existing purchase
    Pg-->>API: ok, no conflict
    API->>Pg: INSERT purchase (PENDING)
    API->>Iyzico: createCheckout({ amount, ref: purchaseId })<br/>(circuit breaker)
    Iyzico-->>API: { checkoutId, redirectUrl }
    API->>Pg: UPDATE purchase SET providerRef
    API->>Pg: COMMIT
    API->>Redis: SET idem:... { status: 'completed', responseBody, 24h }
    API-->>FE: 201 { redirectUrl }

    FE->>Aday: redirect → Iyzico checkout
    Aday->>Iyzico: kart bilgileri + 3DS

    Note right of Iyzico: kullanıcı ödeme tamamladı
    Iyzico->>API: POST /webhooks/iyzico<br/>X-Iyz-Signature: <hash>
    Note over API: verifyIyzicoSignature
    API->>Pg: SELECT WebhookEvent WHERE providerEventId
    Pg-->>API: null (ilk kez)
    API->>Pg: INSERT WebhookEvent (unique)
    API->>Iyzico: GET /payments/<id><br/>(authoritative re-fetch)
    Iyzico-->>API: { status: 'success', amount }
    API->>Pg: UPDATE purchase SET status=ACTIVE
    API->>Pg: INSERT AuditLog action=PURCHASE
    API-->>Iyzico: 200 { received: true }

    Note over FE,API: Frontend polling veya WS ile state güncellenir
    FE->>API: GET /v1/purchases/:id
    API-->>FE: 200 { status: 'ACTIVE' }
    FE->>Aday: ✅ Satın alma onaylandı
